Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responding to an emergency \Nsignal, Luffy and the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,others were heading to the \Nother side of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Nami and the \Nothers were held captive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in a mysterious facility \Non Punk Hazard Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this island to rescue my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind cutting thousands \Nif they get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There!\N--Shoot! Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, that'll be far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save the Children! The \NStraw Hats Start to Fight!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:47.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ICE LANDS - A MYSTERIOUS FACILITY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:53.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,BISCUIT ROOM SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the island's day-care or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so big but are they Giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we come to an island of Giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are not-so-big ones too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's a multi-racial nursery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must be the ones who got frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Frozen?\N--What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery of the island deepens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...A robot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I love robots!\N--They're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The best?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sanji-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robot! Robot! Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robot! Robot! Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kids. So you really love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my armored self?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell me about "the ones who got frozen."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's a stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stuffed racoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Help me!\N--I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky is so popular among boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're right!\N--So weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stag-beetle robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can change my hairstyle as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is another hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pick my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, somebody, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a child named Momonosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The severed-head talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kids, tell me about this facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get any information out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to the Biscuit Room is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming! Let's run to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be those pirates! \NDon't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of facility is this? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a boy named Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got hit by a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dishonor to a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should commit ritual suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! Just stop whining! \NYou male chauvinist pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Those damn escapees!\N--You can't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy! We're not allowed to \Nuse guns and explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use as few gas canisters as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hit a child, the \NMaster will be furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really wanna cross this lake, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:10.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BURNING LANDS LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we cross it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some parts are burning but \Nthere are ice flows as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The temperature could be just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all sweaty so let's swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin and I can't swim so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying I should carry you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Zoro wouldn't wanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already stretching for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, if we don't cross \Nit, we have to go all the way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice. All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack - Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fan Grass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boaty Banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a boat! That's awesome, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can use this Fan Grass as an oar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have many kinds of seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were a whole bunch of weird \Nplants on the Bowin Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deeper I went into the dangerous areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more handy plants I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I survived on that islands for two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no difficulty \Nthat I can't overcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get on board already, Usopp!\N--Or we'll leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm the one who supplied the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the land of snowcones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you rowing, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so windy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There's a headwind!\N--No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a big difference in \Ntemperature on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes for strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water is boiling around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were swimming, it \Nwould've been horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's so slow!\N--Why don't you row then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away! Wait, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That centaur again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you change your mind \Nand decide to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you recruiting again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop asking strange creatures to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy on the Snail said "Boss," too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold... Is this the Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruders are going that \Nway! Please finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something appeared on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the emergency signal \Nwas meant for that Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he shouldn't mean us any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a man with swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is that the samurai who cut our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now kids, move out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay out of the way.\N--It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robot-san! Did you come \Nfrom outside the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course! But I'm \Na cyborg, little guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, our ship - the Sunny is the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is not a day-care?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to help us! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not sick anymore! We are all fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sick? What kind of sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.48,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all scary people! You \Nneed to stay away from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true? They didn't seem like bad people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fooled you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the stag-beetle robot is a villain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Same for Racoon-chan?\N--Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the man with the spiral eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so let us protect you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect you sick kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will put them to sleep \Nwith our cloud guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, please! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kids, you need to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I have to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's take them with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy! We don't even know \Nhow to save ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can take that many kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this?! I have a feeling \N- something tragic is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come back later and help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew! Even if I've never \Nbeen out of this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing on this island, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no city! There is no one else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why nobody comes to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my father and my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.38,0:17:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to help us later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's help these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know for sure they need saving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said those kids are sick \Nso this could be a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just met them and we don't \Nknow what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our job to help every single person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're saying but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't turn your back \Non a child crying for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They'll get away if nothing is done!\N--Those brats are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! Shoot the brats too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But the Master will...\N--Better than letting them go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe Collier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kung Fu Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Racoon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rocket punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stopped running!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind to kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she's only kind \Nto kids but I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling for her even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, you go ahead with Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the beautiful lady \Nand the Kung Fu Racoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight our pursuers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing this to answer Nami-san's \Nbeautiful wish to help you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I don't like you all \Nprecisely because Nami-san
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cares about you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Bro, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, brat! Just run already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They're taking the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do this, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letting down Armored Franky \Nfans is not an option for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.16,0:22:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:29.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow! Snow! I love playing with snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:33.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF THE MYSTERIOUS FACILITY BROOK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great way to kill time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san told me to wait here \Nbut what's taking them so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah! Snowmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rearrange its eyes and nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who is it? Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a torso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and Chopper frantically push through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mysterious facility to save the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While Sanji and Franky fight for their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook is at the mercy of the powerful torso samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until finally, the two begin their duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Swordplay Showdown! Brook vs. \Nthe Mysterious Torso Samurai!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
